OL,6,FThe widow of a man forced to work in
OL,7,Fan slave camp during has been sharing
OL,8,Fdetails of his experience.
OL,10,FIris Prigent says her late husband
OL,11,FGordon struggled to open up about his
OL,12,Fpast - he was just a teenager when he
OL,13,Frefused to work for German soldiers
OL,14,Fand was sent to a concentration camp.
OL,16,FShe explains: "When we got married he
OL,17,Fnever told me that he'd been in a
OL,18,Fconcentration camp, I didn't know, he
OL,19,Fkept it to himself.
