OL,6,F"Then one night he was having a
OL,7,Fnightmare and I said to him, 'Can you
OL,8,Ftell me?'. He said, 'I don't want to'
OL,9,Fand I said, 'Gordon, I think you've
OL,10,Fgot to'."
OL,12,FGordon was sent there alongside
OL,13,Fanother islander, Walter Gallichan,
OL,14,Fwhere what they experienced impacted
OL,15,Ftheir lives.
