OL,6,FChris Addy from Jersey Heritage
OL,7,Fdescribes it: "The harsh working
OL,8,Fconditions and the brutality they
OL,9,Fexperienced had really long-term
OL,10,Feffects on both men, particularly
OL,11,FWalter who spent 30 years in St
OL,12,FSaviours Hospital afterwards."
OL,14,FIris wants Gordon's experience and
OL,15,Fthat of others during the Occupation
OL,16,Fnot to be forgotten.
