OL,6,FShe says: "I think it should be
OL,7,Fremembered, what happened to a lot of
OL,8,Fthe Channel Islanders, not just Gordon
OL,9,F- all the others sent from Guernsey as
OL,10,Fwell - it should be on record so
OL,11,Feverybody knows what happened."
OL,13,FGordon will be remembered through a
OL,14,Fstone placed in Hope Street, St Helier
OL,15,Fwhere he grew up - part of a .
OL,17,FThere are plans to engrave 35
OL,18,FStolpersteine or stumble stones across
OL,19,FJersey and Guernsey with the names and
OL,20,Fmemories of victims and survivors of
OL,21,FNazism.
